					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11957334#post-4646963</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11957334/scp-4855#post-4646963</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2020 19:25:02 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>LunarDelta</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2898811</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>&quot;I mean, I never saw someone tear their own throat out before, you know? And they were still walking, just… running up and down the halls, stabbing each other, painting weird symbols in their own blood…&quot;</p> <p>&quot;It was just garbage words, like word salad, but-&quot;</p> <p>It almost sounds like Ojai Syndrome or some other form of SCP-3125 exposure. Like, this is <em>exactly</em> what happened in &quot;Your Last First Day&quot;. As soon as 3125 descended upon the site the affected/infected people went and got knives so they could cut themselves and each other up, screaming incoherent gibberish while using each other's blood and flesh to create cognitohazardous glyphs.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
